OL,5, The takeover of Britain's largest      
OL,6, microchip plant by a Chinese-owned     
OL,7, company must be reversed, the UK       
OL,8, government has said.                   
OL,10,FNewport Wafer Fab was acquired by      
OL,11,FDutch-based technology company         
OL,12,FNexperia, a subsidiary of Shanghai     
OL,13,Flisted Wingtech, in July 2021.         
OL,15,FHowever, Nexperia must now sell 86% of 
OL,16,Fits stake "to mitigate the risk        
OL,17,Fnational security" following a review. 
OL,19,FThe firm said it was "shocked" and     
OL,20,Fwould appeal against the decision.     
